{'book': {'publisher': 'Amistad', 'synopsis': 'Steve Harvey can’t count the number of impressive women he’s met over the years—women who can run a business, keep a household with three kids in tiptop shape, and chair a church group all at the same time. So when it comes to relationships, why can’t these women figure out what makes men tick? According to Steve, it’s because they’re asking other women for advice when they should be going directly to the source. In his indispensable relationship guide Act Like a Lady, Think Like a Man, now the basis for a major motion picture, Steve lets women inside the male mindset; introduces concepts such as the ninety-day rule; and reveals the five questions women should ask a potential partner to determine how serious he is.<br/>Sometimes funny, sometimes direct, but always truthful, Act Like a Lady, Think Like a Man is a book you must read if you want to understand how men think when it comes to relationships, intimacy, and love.', 'language': 'en', 'image': 'https://images.isbndb.com/covers/09/87/9780062190987.jpg', 'title_long': 'Act Like a Lady, Think Like a Man Movie Tie-in Edition: What Men Really Think About Love, Relationships, Intimacy, and Commitment', 'edition': 'Reprint', 'dimensions': 'Height: 8 Inches, Length: 5.3125 Inches, Weight: 0.40124131684 Pounds, Width: 0.540541 Inches', 'dimensions_structured': {'length': {'unit': 'inches', 'value': 5.3125}, 'width': {'unit': 'inches', 'value': 0.540541}, 'weight': {'unit': 'pounds', 'value': 0.40124131684}, 'height': {'unit': 'inches', 'value': 8}}, 'pages': 240, 'date_published': '2012-01-31', 'subjects': ['Self-Help', 'Relationships', 'Love & Romance', 'Marriage'], 'authors': ['Steve Harvey'], 'title': 'Act Like a Lady, Think Like a Man Movie Tie-in Edition: What Men Really Think About Love, Relationships, Intimacy, and Commitment', 'isbn13': '9780062190987', 'msrp': 13.99, 'binding': 'Paperback', 'isbn': '0062190989', 'isbn10': '0062190989'}}